Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通路給堵塞了 就是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水晶鎖匙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mistral Wind！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才好像美茹的女人是甚麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的過去究竟…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四話  [ 光。影和闇 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恭候多時了 普陸斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何方神聖？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你去 [闇之國] 的嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闇之國？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停…停止…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來 快進來我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？是甚麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…！繼續…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲…厲害…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在這種地方做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…！繼續…不要停…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情在我體內為所欲為吧…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續…用力一點…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…繼續…用力一點…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…普陸斯的佩劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很強壯…厲害…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好舒服…普陸斯…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！功虧一簣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這隻臭怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！妳休想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才迷迷糊糊 謝謝妳救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻怪物是影之一族嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她好像提過甚麼闇之國
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闇之國？那是甚麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快點穿回衣服啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上不只光與影這兩個國家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫莉達
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是傳說中的普陸斯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 你跟那尊石像很似啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 妳為何來到這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是光之一族的女劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看如果跟著你來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許能立功回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的地震是甚麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要爆發戰爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到那個是光與影結合的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之一定要想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一條就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影兩國之間的通路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向法布利陛下報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…緊張得打震罷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又會…爆發戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼！？通路給打通了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們剛剛收到莉達大人的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人把通路的封印解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 原來普陸斯成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決戰的時刻來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向全軍下令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上一舉進攻影之國！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼人！？光之劍士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然妄想踏入我們影之國一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…曾經在這裡戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的光之一族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今次要把他們統統殺光！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聽著！馬上迎擊敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經忍無可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰爭結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向禾斯卡陛下提出我們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒 你是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現在未是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳現在還掛念著艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在20年前已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 吊兒郎當的艾斯托爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法忘記那一天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾！別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想認定他已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾已經死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點忘記他吧！莎朗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 有守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看那個山洞可能是通向底層的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子 我們不用作無謂的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能去到敵人的根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不但劍術高明 人也很聰明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你怎會知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經在這裡出出入入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那沒理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡已經給堵塞了20年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…失去了20年前的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼久的事 我也記不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗 這樣下去不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們暫時退回西門 重整軍勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們比較熟悉地形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到那裡便能夠反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延時間直至重整軍勢為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人走過石橋後便把石橋炸毀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個通風口一直通往那裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個姿勢也令人很累
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有光！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看那邊可能不是出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色鬼！你做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…全因妳突然停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸橋的準備完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 馬上把橋炸毀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光之士兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是通風口！他們從通風口潛入來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝通風口發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逃了 捉住他！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放過他！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我軍被逼回西門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡陛下！你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟來 我想一個人靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告完後便馬上給我回戰場！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正蠢才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他經常在這附近便失去縱影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及時頂住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡那傢伙想去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth 石板還差少許便…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次大事不妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去叫曼查回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟普陸斯失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著怎辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是影之一族嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是影之一族的國王 禾斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真走運呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待我收拾你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搖身一變成為英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 妳能那麼輕易收拾我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看…看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳剛才的威風去了哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？到此為止了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 一劍殺死我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死在影之國王手上 我雖死猶榮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這個女人真勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳當光之劍士實在太可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然妳那麼勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳一定會為我生個勇敢的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…說甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾現在下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只好待我跟妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誕下光與影結合的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為妳是光之一族的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在胡說些甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！即使我是女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是光之劍士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳只好怪自己不是男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停…停手…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一種…古怪的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我好驚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它那麼大…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的會受不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要妳那裡這麼濕便沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱！好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下 別放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！不！停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再回光之國…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 妳就永遠留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊…！停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要繼續嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還未行！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至令妳懷有光與影結合的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體…受不住了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體…愈來愈古怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth 石板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這一塊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽聞它已經給打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直把碎片收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把它還原成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中有這樣的記載
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閱讀這塊石板便會無所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 會讀這塊石板上的文字的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有光與影結合的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那個人會帶來新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影結合的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.42,0:24:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我們不可讓你們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.59,0:24:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達西奧！？\N曼查！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之一族的參謀為何會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.77,0:24:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.19,0:24:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧！禾斯卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.71,0:25:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到光之劍士中有你這種高手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.46,0:25:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.55,0:25:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一招是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.47,0:25:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.08,0:25:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.00,0:26:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說) 第四話完  待續
